reviews.text: Came here for dinner around hooch hour. Ordered some drinks for $5.09 each to start off. My friends had the custom burgers and I had the mussels. Not bad!...
Service was simply amazing. We were taken care of and checked up on frequently! Our waiter was super friendly and established a positive rapport with us...

Great food.
Great service. 
Fun atmosphere - loved the videos!
Looking forward to our next visit.

A trendy looking place that attracts a well dressed happy hour crowd. If you're into 'comfort food' you'll like the menu. The food was very good, and the service was pretty good. That's something of an accomplishment given how busy the place was both times I was there.

Food was delicious. I got the pulled pork grilled cheese. I went during lunch time and the service was slow even though it wasn't busy. Food didn't come out at the same time for our group of 10 people which sucked. It came out with like 10 minutes between the first and last plate. Server must've been new because he seemed confused the whole time. Everyone loved their food though

I've been here many times since this location opened, and I must say that tonight is the best service I've had. Emily was pleasant, fast, and went above and beyond. I really appreciate the excellent service from her tonight. Thank you Emily!

Brought my girlfriend of 2 years here for our anniversary. She's a health nut and was bit concerned but she found plenty of healthy choices. She had the Caveman salad with salmon. Very fresh! Yet still savory. I had the pulled pork grilled cheese sandwich. It was out of this world especially dipped in the cranberry sauce. I made the mistake of sharing with my gf...she ended up eating half and she doesn't even eat sandwiches!  The duck fried sweet potatoes were fabulous appetizer.  2 of us, including 2 glasses of the house....~$100.

I have no problem with an expensive menu, but when the prices are high I expect the food quality to be high as well. I think the food didn't measure up what it should be in that price range. Even though the staff was nice and it's a really nice restaurant, the meals should taste a bit better.
